descriptionHtml:
Hello

Its my first try with skyrim creation kit.
Screens say it all ^_^ Its still WIP but it should be 100% working.
-Camp and house contain all crafting gear
-2 merchants with around 5k gold (blacksmith and apothecary)
-THE VIEW (u have to see it) ^_^
Have FUN and sorry for the stairs ^_^

UPDATE
1. mapmarker is here ^_^
UPDATE 2
1. fixed doors to proper loading ones
2. add 2 merchants -> their position is temporary gonna remodel outdoors and make separate place for them 
UPDATE 3
1. Moved smithy to tower
2. Small bar/shop in front of house in place of smithy (new screen)
3. Few random NPC\'s (idling as anything other breaks them :S)
4. Tweaks to camp look (tent, cooking pot, some flora moved, removed, add)
5. Small bridge close to stairs (its just temp so there is no need for swimming)
6. House have working chimney now
7. There is small fishing camp with pier under Overwatch camp
